{"tid":486594,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鳩嗚團7人參選港區人大：支持香港建海水化淡廠 保障中國供水穩定","createTime":"2017-12-02T04:10:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-03T10:12:02.000Z","uid":136994,"like":51,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9e2adb8357341a5bac18c72b47ee4d537fd53b3e","tid":486594,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T04:10:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171202/57531409\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171202%2F57531409&d=Mqva%2FuzIZq0EH9%2BEaea77Mn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=c09d2ac9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171202%2F57531409&h=06ebb3ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171202/57531409</a><br />\n<br />\n雨傘運動後組成的旺角「鳩嗚團」有6名成員，各自帶著15至16個來自民主派的提名表，報名參選港區人大代表。鳩嗚團代表錢寶芬表示，連同周五已報名的成員，鳩嗚團一共有7人報名參選，其參選宣言是「貢獻中國」，包括要求香港建海水化淡廠，以維護內地同胞的水資源，並形容「參得選就梗係想贏㗎啦！」<br />\n<br />\n錢寶芬表示，參選的成員都有簽署聲明擁護中國憲法和香港基本法、效忠中國香港，因為認為要他們擁護中國憲法「其實係冇問題嘅」，又讚揚中國憲法是「世界上寫得最好嘅憲法之一」，但「個問題係究竟做唔做嘅啫！」他們的政綱中包括推動全民退休保障、落實香港高度自治等。<br />\n<br />\n科大副校長葉玉如亦帶著174個提名報名。首次參選的她透露提名人包括前中大校長劉遵義、李國章、公開大學校長黃玉山、理大校長唐偉章、中總會長蔡冠深，亦包括民主派選委，但未有透露其身份。<br />\n<br />\n被問到其政治立場時，她表示自己是科學家、教育家，今次參選是希望幫助香港推動科研發展，令兩地科學、教育上有更多交流，又稱若能當選會積極參與國家的科研政策，再看看如何令香港做得更好。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n班飯桶泛民學吓嘢啦，成日拎道德光環係冇撚用㗎<br />\n學下真愛聯咁唱紅打黑先有用㗎嘛"},{"pid":"a62a8bf48fedbeeedc65e2759671ff0b524b1b7b","tid":486594,"uid":136994,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T04:18:00.000Z","msg":"支持香港建海水化淡廠 <br />\n保障珠三角地區有充足東江(屎)水供應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ce2d93fe2b220237d206dcf4ecdd9c1c5b791ff","tid":486594,"uid":108266,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T04:22:10.000Z","msg":"試下都好"},{"pid":"feb3f29d888efbbc58da34b401a07dc9c422bdcb","tid":486594,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T04:40:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46f29ba65b521d1d8bc707fad78d0c253db4eaaf","tid":486594,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T14:08:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84109b8b5a6fa431f2eeaa6baea1dea7c784cde5","tid":486594,"uid":22858,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T14:09:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20140419/large/1397909704_7998.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20140419%2Flarge%2F1397909704_7998.jpg&h=d247a553&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"268fb27a1f0f2fb25751d3b91d848e95b8db7c83","tid":486594,"uid":35870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T14:11:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20140419/large/1397909704_7998.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20140419%2Flarge%2F1397909704_7998.jpg&h=d247a553&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n右面條友咁似劉曉波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8766c70a68e72b0f67aa594e3f991abfbd9e016d","tid":486594,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T14:12:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20140419/large/1397909704_7998.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2